---
title: One-Pot Tortilla Soup with Black Beans, Corn, and Bell Pepper
description: Tortilla soup is one of the classics of traditional Mexican cuisine for good reason—it’s just as soul-warming and cozy as your typical tomato and veggie soup, but with the crunch of crispy tortillas and an added whisper of chile heat. Our version also introduces black beans and corn to make it extra hearty, plus avocado and cheddar cheese for a creamy finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w10-r09-f44bc311.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w10-r09-e0af45aa.pdf
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
